com.microsoft.azure.management.sql

Class ReplicationLinkOperationsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.management.sql.ReplicationLinkOperationsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReplicationLinkOperations, ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>

    public class ReplicationLinkOperationsImpl
extends Object
implements ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>, ReplicationLinkOperations
    Represents all the operations for operating on Azure SQL Database Replication Links. Contains operations to: Delete and Retrieve replication links.
